headline.main: No. 8 Louisville Overcomes No. 19 Notre Dame 71-64
headline.print_headline: No. 8 Louisville Overcomes No. 19 Notre Dame 71-64

lead_paragraph: Rebounding dominance helped No. 8 Louisville offset offensive inconsistency and create opportunities that ultimately got the job done against No. 19 Notre Dame.
